snippet.title: Sweave: Bosses gameplay trailer
snippet.description:
A new update for Sweave is live!!
This update includes: 
New Bosses, Daily Rewards, A New Tutorial Mode to help you understand how to play the game, Cleaner UI, New energy system, Bug fixes and Some cool visual effects

Check it out and let's see how far you climb up on the competitive leaderboard!
You can download it now via the links below

iOS: https://apps.apple.com/tr/app/sweave/id1668676287

Android: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.letiarts.swerve&hl=en&gl=US
